RT @madeon : @antpats2 I worked a little bit at home remaking new drums and bass sounds and other details.

But the soul of the song was there long before I joined !

RT @madeon : @antpats2 The song already existed, with a rough production from Bloodpop and co-written by Justin Tranter I believe.

I heard a demo and really loved it ! At first I suggested people I thought would sound good working on the production but eventually Bloodpop invited me directly.

RT @madeon : @antpats2 We ended the day by dancing together to the latest Rain On Me demo - very special moment.

I should mention Rami Yacoub was also there throughout and had brilliant insight.

RT @madeon : @antpats2 It was really great when Gaga came to record final vocals, I hadn’t seen her in years and she was as sweet and graceful as ever - truly one of my favorite artists.

We had an awesome session where she dug deep to deliver breathtaking vocals.
